REQUEST THE VNDIRECT API

Source: R/vndirect.R
getData.Rd

Retrieves historical stock data from the VNDIRECT API for multiple tickers.

getData(.tickers = NULL, .size = 100)

Arguments

.tickers

A character vector of stock symbols.

.size

Length of historical data.

Value

A data frame containing historical stock data for all tickers.

Examples

getData(c('TPB', 'VCB', 'HCM'), 1000)
